    Data Information

    dataInformation.Rmd

    Please find information regarding data extracted for each species and data file formats.

    Location of reports

    All reports were downloaded from

    • Stock Assessment Review Index (SARI)
    • Stock Assessment Support Information (SASINF)

    Input file formats

    All pdf files should have the same format.

    YEAR_SPECIESNAME_LOCATION_REPORTNAME.pdf (Note: 3 underscores)

    eg. 2017_mackerel_GOM-GB-MA_SARC64-18-06.pdf

    • LOCATION defines the location where SPECIESNAME is harvested/sampled (eg, GB, GOM, EastGB, GB-GOM, etc). Use hyphens to separate acronyms/words in LOCATION

    • REPORTNAME defines the source report of the pdf.

    Do not use additional underscores. Underscores will be used to split the pdf name if necessary.

    Output

    Column names in all tables vary across species. No consistency

    Herring

    Biomass, landings, discards extracted Need to determin how to combine (although discards seem pretty small to me, maybe worth ignoring)
